Class MovieDisplaySettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.arc.pds.xml.generated.MovieDisplaySettings
  • public class MovieDisplaySettings
extends java.lang.Object
    The Movie_Display_Settings class provides default values for the display of a multi-banded Array using a software application capable of displaying video content.
